      • getButtons

        List<org.apache.wicket.Component> getButtons()
        Get the list of custom buttons for the form. This buttons will appear next to submit button. All buttons must have their wicket:id="button" and must have a label inside them with wicket:id="label"

        Usage: 

         
 	form.getButtons().add(new AjaxLink<Void>(&quot;button&quot;) {
 		public void onClick(AjaxRequestTarget target) {
 			// do something
 		}
 	}.add(new Label(&quot;label&quot;, "Cancel")));
        Returns:
        the custom buttons list
